install internal controls governing travel and attendance to training programs giving emphasis that the venue of seminars and training programs be limited to areas within the immediate jurisdiction of the LGU; and
submit an explanation as to the absolute necessity of the travel made in Vitalis Villas, Vigan, Ilocos Sur for the evaluation of the Audit Team, otherwise the amount of travel expenses claimed shall be refunded pursuant to NBC No. 563 dated April 22, 2016, EO No. 298, and COA Circular No. 2012-003 dated October 12, 2009.

