require the Municipal Planning and Development Council and Municipal Budget Officer to ensure that the specific projects proposed for local funding are included in the Annual Budget as envisioned in the Local Development Plan and Annual Investment Program which are prepared and approved during the budget preparation in accordance with applicable laws; 
request the Local Sanggunian to pass the proper ordinance specifying the projects to be implemented as authorization for their implementation, if applicable, for those programs or projects described in generic or vague terms in the Annual Budget or AIP;
require the BAC to meticulously and judiciously prepare the APP including approved changes thereto, so that procurements generally proceeded from the approved APP and appropriate procurement modality pursuant to Section 7 of the RIRR of RA No. 9184; 
